{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act37side_level_act37side_08_end","storyGroup":"act37side","storySort":15,"storyDependence":"act37side_level_act37side_08_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"GO-8","storyName":"战火重铸之剑","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"最后赢得胜利的那一战中，蒸汽骑士完成了他最后的使命，而维娜也与消失在蒸汽中的阿勒黛完成了告别。回归当下，为了解决城中诸多难题，维娜决定直面公爵的打压。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act37side/level_act37side_08_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act37side_08","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":13,"next":15,"characters":["摩根","达格达","号角","维娜","因陀罗","查尔斯·林奇","人群中的声音","戴菲恩","费斯特","凯瑟琳","阿勒黛","“铣痕”","退伍典范军","埃利西奥","激动的工人","年迈的工人","远去的声音"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e5/Avg_bg_32_g1_lentiavenue.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":4},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0.5","fadetime":"0","id":5},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":6},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":8},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_writerub","volume":"1","id":9},{"type":"sticker","id":10,"multi":"true","text":"<i>“胜利”。</i>","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":11,"multi":"true","text":"\\n<i>拳台上，它所承载的，是赞美与荣誉。</i>","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":12,"multi":"true","text":"\\n<i>但在战场上，它承载的，却是无数沉重的生命。</i>","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":13},{"type":"sticker","id":14,"multi":"true","text":"<i>食腐者之王的死，给所有目睹那一幕的人，留下了太多的恐惧。我不愿去回忆，也不想把它写进我的书里。</i>","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":15,"multi":"true","text":"\\n<i>那个萨卡兹，不需要我去铭记。</i>","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":16,"multi":"true","text":"\\n<i>但，我会永远缅怀查尔斯·林奇，最后的蒸汽骑士。</i>","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":17},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":18},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_405_1#5$1","duration":"1.5","id":19},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":20},{"type":"dialogue","name":"摩根","text":"......他，已经多久没有动了？","id":21,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_avg_npc_405_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_396_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":22},{"type":"dialogue","name":"达格达","text":"十分钟。","id":23,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/dd/Avg_avg_npc_396_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":24},{"type":"charslot","id":25},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act28side/m_avg_wasteland_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":26,"musicid":0},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_651_1#1$1","focus":"m","duration":"1.5","id":27},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":28},{"type":"text","text":"没有人靠近查尔斯·林奇。","id":29},{"type":"text","text":"在场的所有人都远远地围在一起，半跪着，向最后的蒸汽骑士致以敬意。","id":30},{"type":"text","text":"他就那么直直地矗立在圣王会西部大堂之前，蒸汽从他盔甲的每一丝裂缝中向外喷涌。","id":31},{"type":"text","text":"灼热。不停。","id":32},{"type":"dialog","id":33},{"type":"bgeffect","name":"$eb_steamrelease","layer":"2","id":34},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_steamrelease","id":35},{"type":"bgeffect","layer":"2","id":36},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":37},{"type":"text","text":"宛如心脏跳动的声音。","id":38},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_229_1#1","focus":"m","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"号角","text":"他的身体明明已经在与食腐者的战斗中受到了这么严重的损伤，居然还能维持着站姿......","id":40,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_avg_npc_229_1-1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"支撑他站着的，从来不是他的身体，否则他早该止步在诸王长眠之所里了。","id":42,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c9/Avg_avg_1019_siege2_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":43},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":44},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1.5","id":45},{"type":"delay","time":"3.5","id":46},{"type":"text","text":"维娜向着蒸汽骑士的方向走去，所有人都看到了她的动作。","id":47},{"type":"dialog","id":48},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_155_tiger_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"因陀罗","text":"维娜，不要靠近他！他已经没有理智了！","id":50,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_155_tiger_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"......不，我必须要确认。","id":52,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ca/Avg_avg_1019_siege2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_405_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"摩根","text":"之前在地下他差点杀了你，维娜！","id":54,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b7/Avg_avg_npc_405_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_396_1#12$1","focus":"m","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"达格达","text":"让推进之王去吧。","id":56,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_396_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_396_1#13$1","focus":"m","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"达格达","text":"蒸汽骑士......不，查尔斯·林奇的状态不对劲。她应该也看出来了。","id":58,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b3/Avg_avg_npc_396_1-13$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_405_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"摩根","text":"可是——","id":60,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_npc_405_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_396_1#13$1","focus":"m","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"达格达","text":"相信她。","id":62,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b3/Avg_avg_npc_396_1-13$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_405_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"摩根","text":"......","id":64,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_npc_405_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":65},{"type":"charslot","id":66},{"type":"text","text":"维娜靠近了蒸汽骑士，她能感受到灼人的蒸汽几乎让周围的温度都缓缓升高。","id":67},{"type":"dialog","id":68},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1","duration":"1.5","id":69},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"我从没见过你这样，哪怕是在诸王长眠之所。","id":71,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c9/Avg_avg_1019_siege2_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"战争结束了，你已经守护了你的维多利亚，你的使命已经结束了。","id":72,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c9/Avg_avg_1019_siege2_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":73},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_651_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":74},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_steamrelease","volume":"0.5","id":75},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"5","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":76},{"type":"bgeffect","layer":"2","id":77},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":78},{"type":"dialogue","name":"查尔斯·林奇","text":"（急促的喷气声）","id":79,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/ff/Avg_avg_npc_651_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":80},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"你还在寻找什么，那把剑吗？抱歉，它遗失在了这片战场上的某个地方。","id":81,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c9/Avg_avg_1019_siege2_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":82},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_651_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":83},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_steamrelease","volume":"0.5","id":84},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"5","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":85},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"查尔斯·林奇","text":"（急促的喷气声）","id":87,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/ff/Avg_avg_npc_651_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"或者说，你等的，不是那把剑？","id":89,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_1019_siege2_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":90},{"type":"charslot","id":91},{"type":"text","text":"维娜轻轻地触碰到了蒸汽骑士的甲胄，上面斑驳的痕迹无一不刻录着查尔斯·林奇的经历——","id":92},{"type":"text","text":"宣誓继承称号那天与同僚的比试。","id":93},{"type":"text","text":"征战边陲平叛，在漫天巫术中幸存。","id":94},{"type":"text","text":"诸王长眠之所的背叛。","id":95},{"type":"text","text":"向“荣光”号冲锋，向源石冲锋......","id":96},{"type":"text","text":"查尔斯·林奇从未倒下。","id":97},{"type":"text","text":"查尔斯·林奇永远注视维多利亚。","id":98},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"你在注视着圣王会西部大堂......我知道了。","id":100,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_1019_siege2_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":101},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"不止是你，还有很多人都在注视着那里。","id":102,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ca/Avg_avg_1019_siege2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"text","text":"维娜回望着远处围着的维多利亚人，受伤的，沉默的，兴奋的，哭泣的......","id":103},{"type":"text","text":"人们早已自发围起了一堵绵延不绝的人墙，拦住了外面更加骚动不安的人群。","id":104},{"type":"text","text":"他们都轻声念着不同的名字。","id":105},{"type":"text","text":"“推进之王”。“维娜”。“亚历山德莉娜”。“维多利亚”。","id":106},{"type":"dialog","id":107},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_651_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":108},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_steamrelease","volume":"0.5","id":109},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"5","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":110},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":111},{"type":"dialogue","name":"查尔斯·林奇","text":"（急促的喷气声）","id":112,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/ff/Avg_avg_npc_651_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"我从来都不相信你疯了。","id":114,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_1019_siege2_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":115},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"查尔斯·林奇，这是我们第二次正式见面。","id":116,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_1019_siege2_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"我曾希望，如果能走出那片黑暗，你也能找到想要守护的东西。","id":117,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_1019_siege2_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":118},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"而我们都已经走到了这里......那现在，请等着我回来吧。","id":119,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/00/Avg_avg_1019_siege2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":120},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_651_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":121},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_steamrelease","volume":"0.5","id":122},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"5","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":123},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"查尔斯·林奇","text":"（急促的喷气声）","id":125,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/ff/Avg_avg_npc_651_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":126},{"type":"charslot","id":127},{"type":"text","text":"维娜从蒸汽骑士的身边走过，走上了圣王会西部大堂的台阶，独自走进了大堂的深处。","id":128},{"type":"dialog","id":129},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":130},{"type":"text","text":"时间在流逝。","id":131},{"type":"text","text":"起初，人群静悄悄的，而后声音越来越嘈杂，骚动在蔓延。","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"人群中的声音","text":"为什么这么久？难道里面还有其他的敌人？","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"人群中的声音","text":"我们需不需要去帮忙——","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"人群中的声音","text":"安静！相信亚历山德莉娜殿下！","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"人群中的声音","text":"没有看到连蒸汽骑士大人也在安静等着吗？","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"人群中的声音","text":"听说陛下的王冠就存放在里面。你说，会不会等她出来，我们就有一个新的国王了！","id":137},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"不对劲，按照之前的情报，军事委员会不该有更多的抵抗力量了。","id":139,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/dc/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"里面应该什么都没有才对。","id":140,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/dc/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_155_tiger_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"因陀罗","text":"就这么干耗着吗？我们直接打进去看看不就知道了。","id":142,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f6/Avg_avg_155_tiger_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_405_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"摩根","text":"......","id":144,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_npc_405_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"我去吧。","id":146,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/85/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4162_cathy_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"其他人比你更合适——","id":148,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_4162_cathy_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"奶奶，可只有我们会驾驶“爬行号”。","id":150,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2e/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"有它在，不会有任何危险的。哪怕是对上蒸汽骑士，至少我也有把握自保。","id":151,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2e/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":152},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":153},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1.5","id":154},{"type":"delay","time":"3.5","id":155},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":156},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":157},{"type":"charslot","id":158},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":159},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":160},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":161},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":162},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_writerub","volume":"1","id":163},{"type":"sticker","id":164,"multi":"true","text":"<i>维娜至今没有向我们透露她在圣王会西部大堂里遭遇了什么，我也没有再问费斯特这个问题。</i>","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":165,"multi":"true","text":"\\n<i>那根本不重要。</i>","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":166,"multi":"true","text":"\\n<i>我唯一庆幸的是，在军事委员会的旗帜从圣王会西部大堂的顶端落下后，维娜没有真顶着显眼的王冠走出来。</i>","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":167},{"type":"sticker","id":168,"multi":"true","text":"<i>这才是我的维娜嘛！</i>","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":169,"multi":"true","text":"\\n<i>至少我当时真的是这么认为的......</i>","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":170},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":171},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":172},{"type":"charslot","id":173},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e5/Avg_bg_32_g1_lentiavenue.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":174},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":175},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":176},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":177},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":178},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":179},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":180},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1","focus":"none","id":181},{"type":"dialogue","name":"人群中的声音","text":"她出来了！她出来了！","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"人群中的声音","text":"......王冠呢？她为什么没有戴王冠？","id":183},{"type":"dialogue","name":"人群中的声音","text":"闭嘴，加冕这么重要的事怎么可能这么随意。","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"人群中的声音","text":"可她手里拿的是什么？魔族佬的旗帜？","id":185},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"维多利亚人，食腐者之王已经死了。","id":187,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3e/Avg_avg_1019_siege2_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"我扯下了敌人插在伦蒂尼姆心脏的这一面旗帜。","id":188,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3e/Avg_avg_1019_siege2_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"接下来，我们会砍断每一面萨卡兹留在我们家园的旗帜，驱逐每一个仍然沉溺于嗜血欲望中的敌人！","id":190,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_avg_1019_siege2_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"但请放过手无寸铁的人，放过任何愿意投降的人！","id":191,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_avg_1019_siege2_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"战争已经结束！我们不该用杀戮来审判杀戮，也不该用仇恨来回报仇恨！","id":192,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_avg_1019_siege2_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":193},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"我以维娜·维多利亚的名义向所有为了守卫维多利亚而战的英雄讲话......","id":194,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3e/Avg_avg_1019_siege2_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"我们夺回了伦蒂尼姆，夺回了维多利亚！","id":195,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3e/Avg_avg_1019_siege2_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"而现在，以及不再久远的将来——","id":197,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_avg_1019_siege2_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"我们必将复兴维多利亚！","id":198,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_avg_1019_siege2_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":199},{"type":"charslot","id":200},{"type":"text","text":"维娜高举自己手中的巨锤。","id":201},{"type":"dialog","id":202},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_crwdcheerup","volume":"1","id":203},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":204},{"type":"text","text":"人们站了起来，欢呼的浪潮从中心向外扩散，一浪高过一浪。","id":205},{"type":"text","text":"伦蒂尼姆在为自己的新生而欢庆。","id":206},{"type":"dialog","id":207},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_651_1#1$1","focus":"m","duration":"1.5","id":208},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":209},{"type":"bgeffect","name":"$eb_steamrelease","layer":"2","id":210},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_steamrelease","id":211},{"type":"bgeffect","layer":"2","id":212},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":213},{"type":"text","text":"而浪潮中央，最后的蒸汽骑士也发出了他最后的嘶吼，蒸汽毫不抑制地喷发着。","id":214},{"type":"text","text":"他的心脏不再跳动，那就用燃烧的核心点燃心脏。","id":215},{"type":"text","text":"他的眼睛不再明亮，那就用足以熔化血肉的蒸汽擦亮眼睛——","id":216},{"type":"dialog","id":217},{"type":"bgeffect","name":"$eb_steamrelease","layer":"2","id":218},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_steamrelease","id":219},{"type":"charslot","duration":"2","id":220},{"type":"bgeffect","layer":"2","id":221},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":222},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_mechadown","id":223},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":224},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":225},{"type":"text","text":"然后，他看到了。","id":226},{"type":"text","text":"维多利亚的旗帜与太阳一同闪耀。","id":227},{"type":"text","text":"查尔斯·林奇终于倒下了。","id":228},{"type":"dialog","id":229},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":230},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":231},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":232},{"type":"charslot","id":233},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0","fadetime":"0","id":234},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/ba/Avg_55_i10_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0","id":235},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$distressed_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_distressed_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":236,"musicid":1},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":237},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":238},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":239},{"type":"text","text":"他倒在了黎明曙光里。","id":240},{"type":"text","text":"漫天的蒸汽遮盖了查尔斯·林奇庞大的躯体，甚至没有更多的人注意到他的结局。","id":241},{"type":"text","text":"欢呼的人群中，一道黑色的身影走进了蒸汽之中。阿勒黛为自己曾敬仰的英雄送行。","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"当初，你本可以杀了我。","id":243},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"一个卑劣的人死于所憧憬的英雄之手，本该是故事最好的结局。","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"可，为什么到头来，却是卑劣者为你送行？","id":245},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"......","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"骑士，你的使命结束了。","id":247},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"我的父亲教过我，每一位完成任务光荣凯旋的蒸汽骑士都有扈从为其卸甲并拭去尘埃——","id":248},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"请容我替你卸甲......","id":249},{"type":"dialog","id":250},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_overheat","id":251},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":252},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"......它们早就和你的血肉融为一体。","id":253},{"type":"text","text":"“核心......心脏......冷却......”","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"我会替你保存核心。我向你承诺，你的心脏绝不会停止燃烧，它会替你看到维多利亚的将来——","id":255},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"看到你所要守护的东西被重新擦亮。","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"......蒸汽骑士，你最后的遗言是什么？","id":257},{"type":"dialog","id":258},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":259},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":260},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“从今日起，你将正式享有蒸汽骑士的荣耀。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":261},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“查尔斯·林奇，告诉我，你还想要什么赏赐？”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":262},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“......”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":263},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“陛下，我想要您的剑锋永远锋利。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":264},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“我想要我妻子收获的麦穗年年堆满家门前的粮仓。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":265},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“我想要捧着我刚出生的女儿飞过伦蒂尼姆，俯瞰满城日夜不息的工厂。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":266},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“我想要邻居因为疾病而残废的双腿能重新站起来，和我去喝酒，去歌唱，去给我们相熟的战友彻夜庆功。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":267},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“陛下，我想要的，是生活永远安宁。如果这份赏赐，也需要我自己去争，去斗......”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":268},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“那么，陛下，我向您宣誓——我会一直战斗下去，为了您，为了我所在意的人和我自己，也为了......”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":269},{"type":"subtitle","id":270},{"type":"sticker","id":271,"multi":"true","text":"<i>“......维多利亚。”</i>","x":"295","y":"300","alignment":"center","size":"30","delay":"0.08","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":272},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"“维多利亚。”","id":274},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"查尔斯·林奇的誓言，最后的蒸汽骑士的遗言。","id":275},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"你一生都未曾背弃自己，哪怕被维多利亚所背叛......","id":276},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"呵，“蒸汽骑士”，我的确配不上这个名字，也配不上这副甲胄。","id":277},{"type":"dialog","id":278},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"这场战争，死去的人已经够多了。","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"希望你会是最后一个......再见，查尔斯·林奇——","id":280},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"你听，他们都在为你送行。","id":281},{"type":"text","text":"“维多利亚！胜利！”","id":282},{"type":"text","text":"“维多利亚！！”“为了维多利亚！！！”","id":283},{"type":"dialog","id":284},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_steamrelease","volume":"1","id":285},{"type":"text","text":"“（最后的喷气声）”","id":286},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":287},{"type":"text","text":"“维多利亚”，他最后的那一声嘶哑的呢喃汇入人民呐喊的浪潮中，如同雨水坠向大海，波澜不惊。","id":288},{"type":"text","text":"阿勒黛看到了人群中那些狂热且兴奋的脸，却不禁陷入了沉默。","id":289},{"type":"text","text":"她忍不住遥遥望向了那个站在台阶之上的人，维娜。她确信维娜也看到了自己。","id":290},{"type":"text","text":"维娜只是站在原地，远远地看着她，嘴唇微动。","id":291},{"type":"text","text":"她认出自己了吗？阿勒黛叹了一口气。","id":292},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"你做了正确的选择，也站在了自己该站的位置。","id":293},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"我也一样。","id":294},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“铣痕”","text":"伦蒂尼姆已经不需要更多的英雄了，维娜。","id":295},{"type":"dialog","id":296},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_steamrelease","volume":"0.5","id":297},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":298},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_55_i10_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"3.5","id":299},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.8","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"5.5","block":"true","id":300},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"5.5","block":"true","id":301},{"type":"text","text":"她转身离去，隐入白色的气浪之中。","id":302},{"type":"dialog","id":303},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":304},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":305},{"type":"charslot","id":306},{"type":"image","id":307},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0.5","fadetime":"0","id":308},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e5/Avg_bg_32_g1_lentiavenue.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":309},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1","focus":"all","id":310},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":311},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":312},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":313},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":314},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1","posfrom":"-200,0","posto":"0,0","duration":"1.5","id":315},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":316},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":317},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"维娜，你在看什么？","id":318,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":319},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"......蒸汽骑士的使命完成了，他走了。","id":320,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c9/Avg_avg_1019_siege2_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"——？那些蒸汽，我以为是和过去一样——","id":322,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d6/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"这次不一样。","id":324,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_1019_siege2_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":325},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"那我们......","id":326,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d6/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":327},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"暂时不必去打扰他，正有人为他送行。","id":328,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c9/Avg_avg_1019_siege2_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":329},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"......好。","id":330,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/37/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":331},{"type":"charslot","id":332},{"type":"text","text":"欢庆与哀悼，于此地共存。","id":333},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#11$1","focus":"l","id":334},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":335},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"维娜，接下来，我们该怎么做？","id":336,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":337},{"type":"charslot","id":338},{"type":"text","text":"圣王会西部大堂之前，人们在欢呼，也都不约而同地注视着维娜。","id":339},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#11$1","focus":"l","id":340},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":341},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"他们还在等着你呢。","id":342,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":343},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"......","id":344,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_1019_siege2_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":345},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"我会让他们看到的，戴菲恩。","id":346,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ca/Avg_avg_1019_siege2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":347},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":348},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":349},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2.5","id":350},{"type":"charslot","id":351},{"type":"image","id":352},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0","fadetime":"0","id":353},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_bg_55_g6_dusklentiavenue.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":354},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":355},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act28side/m_avg_wasteland_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":356,"musicid":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":357},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":358},{"type":"animtext","id":359,"name":"group_location_stamp","style":"avg_both","pos":"-400,-200","block":"false","text":"<p=1>西涅塞德大堂前</><p=2>1098年12月25日 5:24 P.M.</>"},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":360},{"type":"animtextclean","id":361},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":362},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_398_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":363},{"type":"dialogue","name":"退伍典范军","text":"......这就是议长的回答吗？她派了你们这些老战友来驱赶我们。","id":364,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_avg_npc_398_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_229_1#1","focus":"m","id":365},{"type":"dialogue","name":"号角","text":"不，值守西涅塞德大堂只是城防军的本职工作之一。纪律就是纪律，霍夫。","id":366,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_avg_npc_229_1-1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_398_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":367},{"type":"dialogue","name":"退伍典范军","text":"英雄不该受到这种对待，黛安和所有流过血的典范军都不该受到这种对待，不是吗，长官？","id":368,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_avg_npc_398_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_229_1#5","focus":"m","id":369},{"type":"dialogue","name":"号角","text":"我明白你的意思，但这不该是议会解决问题的方式。","id":370,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_229_1-5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"号角","text":"这件事不该成为一个先例。","id":371,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_229_1-5.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_398_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":372},{"type":"dialogue","name":"退伍典范军","text":"......我不懂这些，长官。我只知道，黛安是个好人，议会坚持这样做，只会伤了很多人的心。","id":373,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_avg_npc_398_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":374},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":375},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1.5","id":376},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":377},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_229_1#1","focus":"m","id":378},{"type":"dialogue","name":"号角","text":"......你呢，先生？你还是不愿意放弃。","id":379,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_avg_npc_229_1-1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_487_bobb_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":380},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"我很熟悉黛安女士，她绝不是为牟取私利，她本人与维多利亚的贵族势力也绝对没有瓜葛。","id":381,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/93/Avg_avg_487_bobb_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_487_bobb_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":382},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"所以我恳求议长阁下在百忙之中抽出时间，重新考虑对她的审判。","id":383,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3c/Avg_avg_487_bobb_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_229_1#5","focus":"m","id":384},{"type":"dialogue","name":"号角","text":"这是临时法庭做出的判决。黛安无视议会禁令，私闯封锁的王座厅。","id":385,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_229_1-5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"号角","text":"......我们也很熟悉黛安女士。但是，抱歉。","id":386,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_229_1-5.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":387},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":388},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":389},{"type":"charslot","id":390},{"type":"image","id":391},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/63/Avg_bg_32_g4_ordnancefactory.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":392},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":393},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":394},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":395},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":396},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"——黛安？！","id":397,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":398},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的工人","text":"是啊，就是她把我们介绍到你这儿来的！","id":399,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的工人","text":"我们打完仗，家也没了，命也快没了，要不是她一直好言相劝，我现在肯定还在酒桶里醒不过来。","id":400,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的工人","text":"你也觉得她不坏，是不是？只是维娜老大——","id":401,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的工人","text":"维娜议长，该死，我改不了口——她一定是哪里弄错了。","id":402,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的工人","text":"我们都去她办公室找过她了，但我觉得光是人多可能还不够......费斯特老大，你说话更有分量，拜托。","id":403,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":404},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"抱歉，我必须相信一件事，议会对黛安小姐进行了审判，那一定也给了她为自己辩解的权利。","id":405,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/87/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"无论我觉得多奇怪，多不公平，要是维娜能随意改变判决结果，那才是真正的不公平。","id":406,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/87/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":407},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的工人","text":"但黛安应该是不一样的啊......老大，我们好不容易从战争中活下来，她却要因为这么个愚蠢的事去死？","id":408,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":409},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":410},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":411},{"type":"charslot","id":412},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_bg_27_g7_subway.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":413},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":414},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":415},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":416},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4162_cathy_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":417},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"广播和酒馆里都吵得很，听得出来，大部分人不喜欢议会这个决定。","id":418,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_avg_4162_cathy_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_005","focus":"m","id":419},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的工人","text":"你怎么看，凯瑟琳？你说过咱们随时可以向维娜抗议的。","id":420,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4162_cathy_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":421},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"我看，那位黛安女士是个傻姑娘，仅此而已。","id":422,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7f/Avg_avg_4162_cathy_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"她很热心，但她选了最行不通的一种办法。法令是议会自己颁布的，维娜没得选。","id":423,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7f/Avg_avg_4162_cathy_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_005","focus":"m","id":424},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的工人","text":"所以你准备回绝那位医药代表的请求？","id":425,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4162_cathy_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":426},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"我又应该以什么立场去说服议会？","id":427,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_4162_cathy_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_005","focus":"m","id":428},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的工人","text":"......","id":429,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4162_cathy_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":430},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"其实维娜的确有机会解决这个问题，以她的声望，想要说服议会从轻处罚并非不能做到。","id":431,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_avg_4162_cathy_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4162_cathy_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":432},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"不过，有很多双眼睛都在看着她做最后的决定。","id":433,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7f/Avg_avg_4162_cathy_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4162_cathy_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":434},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"伦蒂尼姆议会的议长终归需要面对这些难题。英雄或许可以在战争里救下每一个人，但......","id":435,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/25/Avg_avg_4162_cathy_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":436},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":437},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":438},{"type":"charslot","id":439},{"type":"image","id":440},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/87/Avg_bg_32_g2_dukegarden.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":441},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":442},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":443},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":444},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":445},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_487_bobb_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":446},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"——戴菲恩阁下。","id":447,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/da/Avg_avg_487_bobb_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":448},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"我们花了不少时间找你。","id":449,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_487_bobb_1#11$1","focus":"r","id":450},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"找我？","id":451,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_487_bobb_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":452},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"短短一天，黛安的案件就在伦蒂尼姆城内掀起了巨大的声浪，我们简单调查了一下哪些人在主动散播消息，鼓动市民。","id":453,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_487_bobb_1#11$1","focus":"r","id":454},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"所以......议会想要让我闭嘴。","id":455,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_487_bobb_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":456},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"不，埃利西奥先生，与某些别有所图的推波助澜者相比，你个人的行为其实并没有带来多少影响。","id":457,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"相反，我们都很敬佩你为了一位相识不久的人所做出的努力。","id":458,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_487_bobb_1#11$1","focus":"r","id":459},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"——？","id":460,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_487_bobb_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":461},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"维娜很理解你的心情，她希望亲自来见你，但是被我拦下了。","id":462,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/de/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"抱歉，但现在她的确有更要紧的事需要处理。","id":463,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/de/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_487_bobb_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":464},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"黛安的案子......是不是没有任何转圜的余地？","id":465,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3c/Avg_avg_487_bobb_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":466},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"不。维娜的确可以做到，许多人都清楚这一点。","id":467,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":468},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"说实话，这是一个令人难受的案子。但它的结果会成为议会向所有人宣布的一个信号。","id":469,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_487_bobb_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":470},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"......","id":471,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3c/Avg_avg_487_bobb_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":472},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"我看到你申请查阅过议会的留档记录，那么你应该很清楚黛安女士的罪名、她的自我辩白，以及各位议员对她的看法。","id":473,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/de/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"市民共同制定了伦蒂尼姆现行的新法律，临时法庭依循法律对黛安女士做出了判决，你们在哥伦比亚不是这样做的吗？","id":474,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/de/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_487_bobb_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":475},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"可她也是一位战争英雄，难道不该功过相抵吗？","id":476,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3c/Avg_avg_487_bobb_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":477},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"“功过相抵”......合乎常理，但也充满傲慢的词。","id":478,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":479},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"我总能从史书里看到这个词，而往往能说出这个词的人，都是维多利亚过去的国王。","id":480,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"一旦维娜越过某个界限，而其他人也默许了这件事的发生，那议会存在的意义是什么？","id":481,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"这个议会，和过去那个国王即是议长的议会又有什么区别？","id":482,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":483},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"我没有答案，埃利西奥先生。但我们都不想冒险去找到这个答案。","id":484,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":485},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"议会不会限制你的任何举动。但在黛安这件事上，抱歉，这就是议会的决定，无可更改。","id":486,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/37/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_487_bobb_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":487},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"......黛安没有具体告诉过我，战争中的她是什么样的士兵，大多数时候，她更喜欢描述自己对伦蒂尼姆未来的憧憬。","id":488,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/93/Avg_avg_487_bobb_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"在伦蒂尼姆，我结识的大多数人都对这座城市的未来有着幻梦一般的憧憬。","id":489,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/93/Avg_avg_487_bobb_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":490},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"这是这座城市的幸运，我们能做的，就是不辜负绝大多数人。","id":491,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_487_bobb_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":492},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"......我知道了。","id":493,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/25/Avg_avg_487_bobb_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_487_bobb_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":494},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"黛安坚持种在温室里的药草二月会成熟，听说能够缓解矿石病的剧痛。","id":495,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/69/Avg_avg_487_bobb_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"我会等到那时候，带着一些样本回哥伦比亚研究。","id":496,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/69/Avg_avg_487_bobb_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":497},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"好，在那之前，如果需要帮助，依旧可以联系我们。","id":498,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":499},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":500},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"200,0","duration":"1.5","id":501},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"1","id":502},{"type":"delay","time":"3.5","id":503},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#2$1","focus":"none","id":504},{"type":"dialogue","name":"远去的声音","text":"其实刚来伦蒂尼姆时，我也曾好奇维娜议长会是怎样一个人......","id":505},{"type":"dialog","id":506},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":507},{"type":"delay","time":"3.5","id":508},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":509},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":510},{"type":"charslot","id":511},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_55_i06_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0","id":512},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0.8","fadetime":"0","id":513},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":514},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":515},{"type":"delay","time":"3.5","id":516},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":517},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":518},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_penrustle","volume":"1","id":519},{"type":"sticker","id":520,"multi":"true","text":"<i>每当我和汉娜去学校和疗养院给感染的孩子送去惊喜的时候，他们总是会好奇地问我“亚历山德莉娜殿下的故事”。</i>","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":521,"multi":"true","text":"\\n<i>然后我们会不厌其烦地为他们讲那个街头的混混变成战争中的英雄，最后拯救了伦蒂尼姆的故事。</i>","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":522,"multi":"true","text":"\\n<i>但故事也总会在她走出圣王会西部大堂时戛然而止......后面的故事，不再是适合孩子的童话了。</i>","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":523},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0","fadetime":"10","id":524},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_55_i06_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"10","id":525},{"type":"sticker","id":526,"multi":"true","text":"<i>我多希望那个故事的结局，是维娜脱下那身衣服，和我们一起回到诺伯特区，回到格拉斯哥帮。</i>","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":527,"multi":"true","text":"\\n<i>可我知道那已经不再可能了。</i>","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":528,"multi":"true","text":"\\n<i>在许多人为黛安的遭遇而抗议的那天，维娜详细地向我们解释了她为将要和公爵们召开的会议而准备的提案，涉及食品、医疗、教育、文官系统改革等很多方面。</i>","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":529},{"type":"sticker","id":530,"multi":"true","text":"<i>的确，每一件事维娜都做了正确的决定......但对黛安，她只字未提。</i>","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":531,"multi":"true","text":"\\n<i>我们安静地听完了她所有的想法后才默默离开。</i>","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":532},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":533},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":534},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"燃料统计报告......全城疗养院综合报告......抑制类药物配给清单报告......","id":535},{"type":"dialog","id":536},{"type":"text","text":"维娜的视线回到手头的文书上，努力让那些冗长的文句和数字进入自己的脑海。","id":537},{"type":"text","text":"她知道，再过几分钟，桌上会响起铃声，提醒自己按时前往宴会厅。","id":538},{"type":"text","text":"她也知道，那几位客人并不会真的在乎她尝试背下的这些数字，更不在乎数字背后的生老病死。","id":539},{"type":"text","text":"但她在乎。这一次，是她主动邀请了那几位公爵。","id":540},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"希望这个办法能够奏效。","id":541},{"type":"text","text":"冷清下来的办公室里隐约能听见窗外抗议者的呼喊。","id":542},{"type":"dialog","id":543},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":544},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"......抱歉，黛安。","id":545},{"type":"dialog","id":546},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":547},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3.5","block":"true","id":548},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":549},{"type":"charslot","id":550},{"type":"image","id":551}],"characters":["摩根","达格达","号角","维娜","因陀罗","查尔斯·林奇","人群中的声音","戴菲恩","费斯特","凯瑟琳","阿勒黛","“铣痕”","退伍典范军","埃利西奥","激动的工人","年迈的工人","远去的声音"]}